title: Easy Table Settings for Every Occasion - Noeleen Foster
description: Overview: Many of the most important events of our lives are made even more memorable when we gather with those we love to share a meal, conversation and laughter. Whether the occasion is a special celebration or a simple family meal, a stylish table complements both the food and the company. If you love to entertain, Easy Table Settings for Every Occasion is filled with ideas that will inspire you to create special moments around your dining table. The text includes hints on how to make various decor items, and tips on entertaining with flair.
